Path: godot/classes/class_animatedsprite3d.rst
Summary: Member variables and their default values for the AnimatedSprite3D class

- animation (StringName): The name of the animation to play. Default: &"default"
- autoplay (String): The name of the animation to autoplay. Default: ""
- frame (int): The current frame index. Default: 0
- frame_progress (float): The progress within the current frame. Default: 0.0
- speed_scale (float): The speed multiplier for animations. Default: 1.0
- sprite_frames (SpriteFrames): The SpriteFrames resource containing animations. No default value specified.
